---
title: Herby Halloumi, Beef & Brussels Sprout Toss with Garlic Aioli
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful Mediterranean halloumi and beef meets roasted vegetables tossed with mild spices, with a dollop of tangy aioli to finish it off.

